
# Lab 2: MPI Collective Communication Exercises

### COMPILARE

mpicc Lab2_Ex1a.c -o Lab2_Ex1a
mpicc Lab2_Ex1b.c -o Lab2_Ex1b
mpicc Lab2_Ex2.c  -o Lab2_Ex2
mpicc Lab2_Ex3.c  -o Lab2_Ex3

### EXERCITIUL 1a: Cautarea cu MPI_Bcast + MPI_Reduce (MAX)

Descriere: Cauta un element intr-un tablou. Afiseaza indexul MAXIM.

--- Test cu 2 procese ---
mpirun -np 2 ./Lab2_Ex1a

--- Test cu 4 procese (standard) ---
mpirun -np 4 ./Lab2_Ex1a

--- Test cu 8 procese (demonstreaza load balancing pe mai multi procesori) ---
mpirun -np 8 ./Lab2_Ex1a

--- Test pe localhost doar (restrictie topologie) ---
mpirun -np 4 --host localhost ./Lab2_Ex1a

### EXERCITIUL 1b: Cautarea cu MPI_Scatter + MPI_Gather

Descriere: Cauta element. Afiseaza TOATE pozitiile si care proces a gata-o.

--- Test cu 2 procese (show parallelism overhead) ---
mpirun -np 2 ./Lab2_Ex1b

--- Test cu 4 procese (balanced load per processor) ---
mpirun -np 4 ./Lab2_Ex1b

--- Test cu 5 procese (unequal distribution - 20 elemente / 5 ranks) ---
mpirun -np 5 ./Lab2_Ex1b

--- Test cu single process (sequential baseline) ---
mpirun -np 1 ./Lab2_Ex1b

### EXERCITIUL 2: Adunare matrici cu MPI_Scatter + MPI_Gather

Descriere: Aduna doua matrici (4x5). Valideaza rezultatul.

--- Test cu 2 procese (2 linii per proces) ---
mpirun -np 2 ./Lab2_Ex2

--- Test cu 4 procese (1 linie per proces) ---
mpirun -np 4 ./Lab2_Ex2

--- Test minimal: single rank (no distribution overhead) ---
mpirun -np 1 ./Lab2_Ex2

--- Test maximal: 8 ranks (more processes than rows, some idle) ---
mpirun -np 8 ./Lab2_Ex2

### EXERCITIUL 3: Inversare culori imagine RGBA cu MPI_Scatter + MPI_Gather

Descriere: Inverseaza RGB, pastreaza Alpha. Testeaza imagini de diferite dimensiuni.

--- Test cu 2 procese (simple, few pixels) ---
mpirun -np 2 ./Lab2_Ex3

--- Test cu 4 procese (standard) ---
mpirun -np 4 ./Lab2_Ex3

--- Test cu 8 procese (demonstreaza graceful degradation cu putini pixeli) ---
mpirun -np 8 ./Lab2_Ex3

--- Test binding to cores (optimizare performanta) ---
mpirun -np 4 --bind-to core ./Lab2_Ex3

### TESTE AVANSATE (SETARI MPI DIVERSE)

--- Toate exercitiile cu verbose output ---
mpirun -np 4 -v ./Lab2_Ex1a
mpirun -np 4 -v ./Lab2_Ex1b
mpirun -np 4 -v ./Lab2_Ex2
mpirun -np 4 -v ./Lab2_Ex3

--- Teste cu error propagation check (MPI_Abort safety) ---
mpirun -np 3 ./Lab2_Ex1b  # 20 elemete / 3 ranks - verificare erori

--- Performance comparison: sequential vs parallel ---
echo "Sequential (1 rank):" && mpirun -np 1 ./Lab2_Ex2
echo "Parallel 4 ranks:"    && mpirun -np 4 ./Lab2_Ex2
echo "Parallel 2 ranks:"    && mpirun -np 2 ./Lab2_Ex2

